citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 pm on 06-FEB-
2024. Upon arrival at the home, called the licensee and left a message. Went to the door and was told the licensee had
moved and no longer lived there.
End Section
